title: Jerry Jones, Lamar Jackson, Browns, and Rams
itunes:title: Jerry Jones, Lamar Jackson, Browns, and Rams
description:
Colin explains why the biggest issue preventing the Cowboys from going forward is Jerry Jones, why Lamar Jackson is a target and needs to be careful, why the Browns are upset with Baker Mayfield, and why the Rams need Todd Gurley to be healthy to succeed. Guests include Nick Wright, Solomon Wilcots, Drew Bledsoe, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
